        "@id": "https://doi.org/10.18129/B9.bioc.Rigraphlib"
      },
      "sc:description": "Vendors the igraph C source code and builds it into a static library. Other Bioconductor packages can link to libigraph.a in their own C/C++ code. This is intended for packages wrapping C/C++ libraries that depend on the igraph C library and cannot be easily adapted to use the igraph R package.",
